│ implementation modifies the original compare instruction directly, which is   │
│ shared by both header and latch branches. This unintentionally changes the    │
│ header's control flow one iteration earlier than intended, potentially        │
│ violating assumptions made by peeling and confusing correctness checks        │
│ (Alive2 reports the source may not reach a return under its analysis          │
