│ the mutation affects both branches.                                           │
│                                                                               │
│ 3. Root Cause Analysis:                                                       │
│ The code in LoopPeel.cpp, when PeelLast is true, obtains the compare          │
│ (ICmpInst) by reading the latch branch's condition, and then mutates the RHS  │
│ of that ICmp in-place. This assumes the compare is only consumed by the latch │
